## Academic Use Notice

This software is provided for academic research and educational purposes only.
The authors explicitly disclaim any responsibility for misuse of this software
for breaking real-world encryption systems.

The research demonstrates NEGATIVE results - showing that Neural ODEs FAIL to
break ARX ciphers. This is intended to validate cipher designs, not compromise
them.

By using this software, you agree to:
1. Use it only for legitimate academic research
2. Not use it to attack real-world systems without authorization
3. Cite the original research when publishing results
4. Report any vulnerabilities discovered responsibly